description:
Intelligent Cloud Customer Service Expert

NetEase QIYU is a SaaS cloud customer service product under NetEase, dedicated to reducing enterprise management costs, improving customer satisfaction, and solving problems for customers anytime, anywhere through self-developed customer service robots. With the product creed of "QIYU changes customer service, service creates value," it provides a complete set of service solutions for enterprises in terms of customer service efficiency, customer service awareness, and customer service specialization.
